{"tid":1934800,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(大約是冬季) 泰國新增50宗確診　馬國明將派軍隊協助執行封城令","createTime":"2020-03-20T07:15:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T07:12:42.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"fc5bd565f062dd353c4b358c5c60573b0707d9bf","tid":1934800,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T07:15:15.000Z","msg":"新型肺炎持續在東南亞蔓延，泰國新增50宗確診病例，累計個案增至322宗，一人死亡，大部分位於首都曼谷，其中41宗新增個案與早前確診病例有關，另外9宗是輸入個案或與外國旅客有密切接觸。<br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞政府宣布，星期日開始派遣軍隊協助警方執行限制出行令，以遏制病毒傳播。國防部長批評，民眾不理會當局要求留在家中的命令，繼續前往餐廳及公園，有必要派士兵協助執法，如果有人繼續違反命令，將採取法律行動。<br />\n<br />\n大馬至今有900宗確診病例，兩人死亡，大部分病例與上月在吉隆坡有16000人參與的清真寺活動有關。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1515773-20200320.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1515773-20200320.htm&d=wsLpXOxElywvcqXyO2fdBGrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=59f69c43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1515773-20200320.htm&h=95d6bc1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1515773-20200320.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f7bf2c048b9af72bfe6fdeeaead220f9f0d83337","tid":1934800,"uid":43845,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T07:15:42.000Z","msg":"又馬國明"},{"pid":"1fb0827956ab910c25052d36401ba3427fe1629e","tid":1934800,"uid":341619,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T07:15:53.000Z","msg":"馬明全能到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"238e970332f13c4b365f7652da4f5dfec75655e6","tid":1934800,"uid":144626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T07:15:55.000Z","msg":"馬國明將派軍隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f88b3f289181a5384352a3f3ecc8af706a60